<div class="alert alert-info">
    ASN stands for Autonomous System Number, which is (essentially) the ISP or Telephone company that controls your IP address.
    Due to company mergers/buyouts/etc, the company name in the database is often a predecesoor of the current company.
    <a class="alert-link" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Autonomous_system_(Internet)">Wikipedia</a>.
</div>

{{#if asndata}}
<h2>ASN for {{ipaddress}}</h2>
<table class="table table-striped border-bottom">
    <tbody>
        <tr>
            <td>Autonomous System Number</td>
            <td>{{asndata.autonomous_system_number}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Autonomous System Organization</td>
            <td>{{asndata.autonomous_system_organization}}</td>
        </tr>
    </tbody>
</table>
{{/if}}
<h2>ASN Lookup for a specific IP</h2>
<div class="container d-flex flex-column">
    <div class="row align-items-center justify-content-center no-gutters">
        <div class="col-12 col-md-5 col-lg-4 py-8 py-md-11">
            <form action="/ip/asn-lookup.html" class="mb-6" method="GET">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="ipaddress">
                        IP Address
                    </label>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="ipaddress" name="ipaddress" placeholder="" value="{{ipaddress}}" />
                </div>
                <button class="btn btn-block btn-primary" type="submit">
                    Check
                </button>

            </form>
        </div>
    </div> <!-- / .row -->
</div> <!-- / .container -->
